:57.000Z","msg":"改名要有改名契先<br />\n唔可以就咁係換身分證果陣順便改"},{"pid":"7eb45750f3d4f4ecaa81964d93608fbb3b16e14d","tid":2507162,"uid":381305,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"如果十八歲換成人身分證，印象中可以免費加英文名，之後上律師樓做改名契。<br />\n如果換左成人身分證之後想改名，就要做改名契同比$390 換身分證。其實證件都要改<br />\n英文名如果跟外國有first name, middle name 同 last name. 正統上應該係Wong, Julian Tai Man. Last name 係wong, first name 係 Julian, middle name 係tai man. 鬼佬只會叫你first name 同 last name. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Julian Wong. 如果你改wong, tai man julian 就叫你tai wong. 把心一橫可以冇middle name 就 Wong, Julian"},{"pid":"ab531f9c0ae9a0895d7807a3d61447586b5a4e62","tid":2507162,"uid":249525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:12:45.000Z","msg":"穩陣起見<br />\n個人認為 留番個舊名做少少連繫<br />\n例如Julian T.M. Wong<br />\n鬼佬只著重first name 同last name<br />\n中間嗰啲唔理你"},{"pid":"69085a5219e6e8440fee66cb493b2866879b67f8","tid":2507162,"uid":363016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab531f9c0ae9a0895d7807a3d61447586b5a4e62","tid":2507162,"uid":249525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:12:45.000Z","msg":"穩陣起見<br />\n個人認為 留番個舊名做少少連繫<br />\n例如Julian T.M. Wong<br />\n鬼佬只著重first name 同last name<br />\n中間嗰啲唔理你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:18:37.000Z","msg":"我需要anglicisation我嘅名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，包括surname。 中文姓/名唔變"},{"pid":"0cb6649fa474a470c6026bdfc012348fec12dc21","tid":2507162,"uid":249525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69085a5219e6e8440fee66cb493b2866879b67f8","tid":2507162,"uid":363016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab531f9c0ae9a0895d7807a3d61447586b5a4e62","tid":2507162,"uid":249525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:12:45.000Z","msg":"穩陣起見<br />\n個人認為 留番個舊名做少少連繫<br />\n例如Julian T.M. Wong<br />\n鬼佬只著重first name 同last name<br />\n中間嗰啲唔理你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:18:37.000Z","msg":"